source.name: FY11_Insurance Dividends by State and County
source.description: The Dividends by State and County dataset provides the amount of insurance dividends paid in CY 2010 by state and county.  The data is reported at the state level, plus insureds in Military America, Military Europe, Military Pacific, American Samoa, Federated States of Micronesia, Guam, Marshall Islands, Northern Mariana Islands, Puerto Rico, and the Virgin Islands.
